26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_bios_vmap.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include <subdev/bios.h>
30#include <subdev/bios/bit.h>
31#include <subdev/bios/vmap.h>
32
33u16
34nvbios_vmap_table(struct nvkm_bios *bios, u8 *ver, u8 *hdr, u8 *cnt, u8 *len)
35{
36 struct bit_entry bit_P;
37 u16 vmap = 0x0000;
38
39 if (!bit_entry(bios, 'P', &bit_P)) {
40 if (bit_P.version == 2) {
41 vmap = nvbios_rd16(bios, bit_P.offset + 0x20);
42 if (vmap) {
43 *ver = nvbios_rd08(bios, vmap + 0);
44 switch (*ver) {
45 case 0x10:
46 case 0x20:
47 *hdr = nvbios_rd08(bios, vmap + 1);
48 *cnt = nvbios_rd08(bios, vmap + 3);
49 *len = nvbios_rd08(bios, vmap + 2);
50 return vmap;
51 default:
52 break;
53 }
54 }
55 }
56 }
57
58 return 0x0000;
59}
60
61u16
62nvbios_vmap_parse(struct nvkm_bios *bios, u8 *ver, u8 *hdr, u8 *cnt, u8 *len,
63 struct nvbios_vmap *info)
64{
65 u16 vmap = nvbios_vmap_table(bios, ver, hdr, cnt, len);
66 memset(info, 0x00, sizeof(*info));
67 switch (!!vmap * *ver) {
68 case 0x10:
69 case 0x20:
70 break;
71 }
72 return vmap;
73}
74
75u16
76nvbios_vmap_entry(struct nvkm_bios *bios, int idx, u8 *ver, u8 *len)
77{
78 u8 hdr, cnt;
79 u16 vmap = nvbios_vmap_table(bios, ver, &hdr, &cnt, len);
80 if (vmap && idx < cnt) {
81 vmap = vmap + hdr + (idx * *len);
82 return vmap;
83 }
84 return 0x0000;
85}
86
87u16
88nvbios_vmap_entry_parse(struct nvkm_bios *bios, int idx, u8 *ver, u8 *len,
89 struct nvbios_vmap_entry *info)
90{
91 u16 vmap = nvbios_vmap_entry(bios, idx, ver, len);
92 memset(info, 0x00, sizeof(*info));
93 switch (!!vmap * *ver) {
94 case 0x10:
95 info->link = 0xff;
96 info->min = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x00);
97 info->max = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x04);
98 info->arg[0] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x08);
99 info->arg[1] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x0c);
100 info->arg[2] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x10);
101 break;
102 case 0x20:
103 info->unk0 = nvbios_rd08(bios, vmap + 0x00);
104 info->link = nvbios_rd08(bios, vmap + 0x01);
105 info->min = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x02);
106 info->max = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x06);
107 info->arg[0] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x0a);
108 info->arg[1] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x0e);
109 info->arg[2] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x12);
110 info->arg[3] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x16);
111 info->arg[4] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x1a);
112 info->arg[5] = nvbios_rd32(bios, vmap + 0x1e);
113 break;
114 }
115 return vmap;
116}
